        Main Constructor
        Parameters:
        onsetInTicks - When the notes starts
        durationInTicks - How long the note is held for
        pitch - Pitch of the note
        channel - MIDI channel it is played on
        track - MIDI track it is played on
        string - The physical guitar string to be played (set to -1 initially)
        fret - The physical fret of the note that will be played (set to -1 initially)
